<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Product Positioning — Work With Me</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Prata&family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/shared/shared.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/studio/studio.css">
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <nav class="container">
    <a href="/" class="nav-name">Mahdi Singaparado</a>
    <button class="nav-toggle" id="navToggle" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="navLinks">Menu</button>
    <div class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
      <a href="/#practice">Practice</a>
      <a href="/#work">Work</a>
      <a href="/#contact">Contact</a>
      <a href="/studio" class="nav-cta">Studio</a>
    </div>
  </nav>
</header>

<main>
  <section class="form-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/studio" class="form-back">← Back to Studio</a>
      <p class="eyebrow">03 · $2,500 – $6,000</p>
      <h1>Product Positioning</h1>
      <p>Tell me about the product and where explanation keeps breaking down. I'll follow up within two business days with scope and a fixed quote.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <form class="intake-form" action="https://formspree.io/f/YOUR_FORM_ID" method="POST">
        <input type="hidden" name="service" value="Product Positioning">

        <div class="field-row">
          <div class="field">
            <label for="name">Name</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="email">Email</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="field">
          <label for="company">Company / Product</label>
          <input type="text" id="company" name="company">
        </div>

        <div class="field">
          <label for="url">Website or product link</label>
          <input type="url" id="url" name="url" placeholder="https://">
        </div>

        <div class="field">
          <label for="problem">Where does the explanation break down?</label>
          <textarea id="problem" name="problem" placeholder="e.g. 'people ask what we do three times before it clicks,' 'investors don't get why this is different,' 'sales calls start with 20 minutes of context'..."></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="field">
          <label for="audience">Who's the buyer, exactly?</label>
          <input type="text" id="audience" name="audience" placeholder="e.g. VP of Engineering at Series A startups">
        </div>

        <div class="field-row">
          <div class="field">
            <label for="budget">Budget range</label>
            <select id="budget" name="budget">
              <option>$2,500 – $4,000</option>
              <option>$4,000 – $6,000</option>
              <option>Not sure yet</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="timeline">Timeline</label>
            <select id="timeline" name="timeline">
              <option>Within 2–3 weeks</option>
              <option>Within a month</option>
              <option>No rush</option>
            </select>
          </div>
        </div>

        <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Send request →</button>
        <p class="form-note">This goes directly to my inbox. No account, no spam.</p>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<footer>
  <div class="container footer-row">
    <span>© 2026 Mahdi Singaparado</span>
    <div class="footer-links">
      <a href="/">Practice</a>
      <a href="/studio">Studio</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<script src="/shared/shared.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
